They have done many upgrades, including new windows, flooring,  Brand New Stainless steel Appliances, Master Shower and Brand New Water Filtration System. Large open Kitchen, split bedroom. Large master bedroom. New Washer and Dryer to Stay. New Walk in shower. This beautiful home is located directly by a parks and waterway. Enjoy your gorgeous back yard overlooking water. This home is NOT in a Fema Flood Zone. Certification is on file. Engineer letter of permanent foundation is also on file.
